condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section 1, D, 1 | Description :Prepare, submit for review, disclose and adopt the ESMF and RPF | DueDate :01-Aug-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section 1, E 5 | Description :If the Project develops into any geographical areas not covered by theexisting ESMF and/or RPF, the ESMF and/or RPF as the case may be, shall be updated not later than six motnhs after the Effectivedate and prior to commencement of LIPW.
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section 2, A | Description :Six month progress report shall be prepared not later than 45 days afterthe period. | Frequency :SemiAnnual
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, A, 2 (c) | Description :A M&E Specialist and additional administrative support as neededto assume their duties in the PIU | Due Date :01-Aug-2012
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, A, 2 | Description :Recurit an internal auditor | Due Date :01-Apr-2012
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, A, 3 (a) | Description :Engage a Delegated Contract Manager prior to commencement ofactivities under Part A of the project | Due Date :15-Jul-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, A, 4 (a) | Description :Engage a Service Provider prior to the commencement of anyactivities under each Parts B (i) through B (v) of the project | Due Date :15-Jul-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, B, 1, a; Schedule 2, Section I, B, 1, b | Description :Employment of delegate contractmanagers and service providers for each sector covered by the public works program and for each skills development activity underpart B of the project, prior to commencement of the program in the sector or activity concerned.
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, C, 1 | Description :Prepare, submit for IDA's review and adopt a Financial andAdministrative Procedure Manual | Due Date :01-Feb-2012
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, C, 2 | Description :Prepare, submit for IDA's review and adopt a Project ImplementationManual | Due Date :01-Apr-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, D, 1 | Description :Update the current financial management manual to reflect theadditional financing not later than 2 months after the Effective Date. | Due Date :15-Aug-2015
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, D, 2 | Description :Update Project Implementation Manual (PIM) not later than 3 monthsafter the effecitve date. | Due Date :15-Sep-2015

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, E, 1 | Description :Prepare and furnish for IDA's review and approval an annual work planof activities proposed for inclusion in the project during the following calendar year no later than Sept. 30 each year. |Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, E, 4 | Description :Adoption of ESMPs and RAPs prior to commencing activity.

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, F, 1 | Description :Preparation and furnishing to the association of an annual work planof activities proposed for inclusion in the project the following calendar year (including budget, and all safeguard instrumentsforsuch activities) and a timetable for their implementation not later than September 30 of each year. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, A | Description :Prepare and furnish to IDA project reports covering a 1 calendarsemester period no later than 45 days after the end of such period. | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B, 2 | Description :Prepare and furnish not later than f45 days after the end of eachcalendar quarter, interim unaudited financial reports for the Project covering the quarter. | Frequency :Quarterly
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B, 3 | Description :Recipient shall have financial statements audited annually not laterthan 6 months after the period. | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B, 4 | Description :No later than 3 months after effective date recruit one additionalaccountant. | Due Date :15-Sep-2015
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B, 4 | Description :No later than 4 months after effective date engage an externalauditor. | Due Date :15-Oct-2015
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B, 4 | Description :Procure and install accounting software | Due Date :01-Feb-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B, 4 | Description :Reconfigure the existing accounting software to reflect theadditional financing not later than 2 months after the effective date. | Due Date :15-Aug-2015
